description:
NodePerformance:  Table containing performance data for radio access network nodes, including timestamps, location, node identifiers, and (mostly placeholder) performance metrics.

dateTime: Timestamp of the performance data record.
Area_Name: Geographic area of the node.
CellId: Unique identifier for the cell site.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  An ID field with currently only one value (1).
vsDataType:  Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
NodePerformance.zzzTemporary1-8: Placeholder columns; likely intended for future performance metrics.
NodePerformance.nodePerformanceId: Unique identifier for the performance data record.
